-- BDO Seidman Said to Enter Deferred Prosecution Deal With U.S.
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2012-06-13T19:23:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-13/bdo-seidman-said-to-enter-deferred-prosecution-deal-with-u-s-.html
Accounting firm BDO Seidman LLP has
entered into a deferred prosecution agreement with the federal
government as part of the biggest tax-fraud prosecution in U.S.
history, a person familiar with the matter said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
